data.name: VelcroftSMP
data.description:
Velcroft SMP is Finally LIVE! 

 📣  We're excited to announce that Velcroft SMP is officially up and running! For the past week, we have been working tirelessly to make this server as cool as possible for every one of y'all!

Featuresss:
 ❤️ Lifesteal – if you dont know what that is basically its like where when u kill someone you get one of their hearts and when they kill u its vice versa!,
 💬 like a million different commands, pretty much any command u can think of  like /spawn, /tpa, /home (after doing /sethome first ofc) and wayyyyyy more!,
 🏪   There are also really cool sections in /shop and theres other plugins to help you build rly cool stuff, also u can earn money/materials by afking in the AFK pool,
🦅  We are proud to announce Eagler support! You can now join from Eaglercraft 1.8.8!

 💻  IP: velcroftsmp.xyz

JOIN NOWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWWW!
